{"tid":235380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男生闖中大校園女生宿舍裸跑","createTime":"2017-05-09T03:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T05:10:48.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f185f8f90d60926b85656c9e4de706e19760874","tid":235380,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:29:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">男生闖中大校園女生宿舍裸跑</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170509/s00001/2bf10aaf0bdd1088a008e63c5e4ffd67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170509%2Fs00001%2F2bf10aaf0bdd1088a008e63c5e4ffd67.jpg&h=7bdea116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文大學發生學生裸跑案。凌晨4時許，一名年約20歲男生被發現在陳震夏宿舍祼跑，其間闖入女生宿舍樓層，警員接報到場截獲該男生，救護員為他披上毛氈，由救護車將他送院治理，在場調查原因。早上8時許，警員在宿舍帶走另一名男生助查。其後有一名女生報稱感到身體不適，送院檢驗。 <br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，警員調查期間，在宿舍檢獲少量毒品，懷疑與案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170509/s00001/1494290958732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170509%2Fs00001%2F1494290958732&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5e9fe6fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170509%2Fs00001%2F1494290958732&h=5d7ad7d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170509/s00001/1494290958732</a>"},{"pid":"e99ddbe462f994bf7f5d548ad470b20e37ed849f","tid":235380,"uid":2111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"條女不乜撚野適呀"},{"pid":"aff28e731627113de53ea4e5f2e0b7c917ca045a","tid":235380,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條女不乜撚野適呀</blockquote><br />\n濕左唔舒服掛"},{"pid":"7b06ecd40fa32cfc154b1fec8bdb771b48f2e2d6","tid":235380,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re